      <title>软银集团股价创1998年上市以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/softbank-group-shares-plunge-most-since-going-public-in-1998</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，日本股市暴跌导致软银集团公司市值蒸发 150 亿美元，创下自 1998 年创始人孙正义带领公司上市以来的最大单日跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/softbank-group-shares-plunge-most-since-going-public-in-1998</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 07:23:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称玛氏公司正考虑收购全球零食制造商 Kellanova</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/mars-is-said-to-consider-acquiring-global-snacks-maker-kellanova</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，美国少数族裔糖果公司玛氏公司 (Mars Inc.) 正在考虑收购零食制造商 Kellanova，这可能是今年消费品行业最大的交易之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/mars-is-said-to-consider-acquiring-global-snacks-maker-kellanova</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 07:20:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其消费者通胀放缓速度创 2022 年以来新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/turkish-consumer-inflation-slows-at-sharpest-pace-since-2022</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其7月份整体通胀率出现近两年来最大幅度下降，这一放缓主要是由于基数效应，而官员们可能因为关注更直接的价格风险而忽视了这一效应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/turkish-consumer-inflation-slows-at-sharpest-pace-since-2022</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 07:02:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
